Subject: VBO:0300002
Value: Breed recognition status referring to a breed recognized by an international organization. This status also refers to breeds that are eligible to compete in championship classes.

Subject: VBO:0300004
Value: Breed recognition status referring to a breed that is reported by an international organization but not recognized.

Subject: VBO:0300010
Value: Extinction status given to a group of animals in which the number of breeding males and/or females is sufficient to maintain the existence of the breed.

Subject: VBO:0300011
Value: Extinction status given to a group of animals in which the breeding population (ie number of breeding males and/or females, and/or the number of living animals belonging to a breed) is reduced to a level that is threatening the existence of the breed.
